<h2>Details</h2>
<p>The BIGSdb software is written in Perl, also utilizing some client-side Javascript.  It runs on Linux using the <a href="http://www.apache.org/">Apache</a> web server and <a href="http://www.postgresql.org/"> PostgreSQL</a> database.</p>
<p>BIGSdb is open-source software, published under the <a href="http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl.html"> GNU General Public Licence version 3</a>.</p>
